OL,3,CCalls for Westminster to step in as
OL,4,Cnurses say patients are 'dying in
OL,5,Ccorridors'
OL,7,FRCN Northern Ireland Executive
OL,8,FDirector, Professor Rita Devlin said:
OL,9,F"Our nurses are spending their shifts
OL,10,Fapologising to patients because they
OL,11,Fcannot deliver care.
OL,13,F"They are ashamed of the care that
OL,14,Fthey are delivering because that is
OL,15,Fnot what they came into nursing for.
OL,16,FPatients at end of life are being
OL,17,Fcared for in a corridor.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
