OL,3,CCalls for Westminster to step in as
OL,4,Cnurses say patients are 'dying in
OL,5,Ccorridors'
OL,7,F"Older people in distress, constant
OL,8,Fnoise, a constant environment where
OL,9,Fthey are becoming distressed and
OL,10,Fconfused. That is leading to those
OL,11,Fpatients needing more care in the
OL,12,Flonger term.
OL,14,F"This report tells of the patient's
OL,15,Fstory but it also tells the lived
OL,16,Fexperience of our nurses and what it
OL,17,Fis like to actually try to care for
OL,18,Fpatients in environments that are
OL,19,Fcompletely unsuitable."
