OL,3,CCalls for Westminster to step in as
OL,4,Cnurses say patients are 'dying in
OL,5,Ccorridors'
OL,7,FA Stormont Health Committee on
OL,8,FThursday heard that the Department is
OL,9,Ffacing a #400million pound funding gap
OL,10,Fwhich could make it difficult to
OL,11,Fdeliver pay awards for healthcare
OL,12,Fprofessionals.
OL,14,FBrigette Worth, Department of Health,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We know that delivering another
OL,16,F#200million in savings on top of the
OL,17,F#200million delivered last year would
OL,18,Fbe incredibly challenging for the
OL,19,Ftrusts.
