OL,3,CCalls for Westminster to step in as
OL,4,Cnurses say patients are 'dying in
OL,5,Ccorridors'
OL,7,F"There will probably come a time
OL,8,Fwhenever we have to make a choice
OL,9,Fbetween services and pay."
OL,11,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt entered a
OL,12,Fbid for #35million for health service
OL,13,Fpay awards in the re-organisation of
OL,14,FExecutive funds known as the January
OL,15,Fmonitoring round.
OL,17,FHe was instead awarded #7million which
OL,18,Fwill go towards settling last year's
OL,19,Fpay disputes.
